pageTitle: Itinerary for Saturday, January 23, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Saturday, January 23, 2016:

Davos-Klosters

The Prime Minister will be in private meetings at the World Economic Forum in the morning.

Davos-Klosters

9:30 a.m. EST/3:30 p.m. CET  The Prime Minister will depart Davos-Klosters for Ottawa.

PMO Media Relations: 613-957-5555
